er than fixing a possible issue before it came an issue, they included this kind of crap on him. That tells me they anticipated a problem, COULD have fixed it, and didn't.  Thats not a human mistake. In my eye, thats incompetance.  Thats all I have to say about that...<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Nov 13 23:29:57 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>~Hanel~<br>Your friendly neighborhood Barbarian on 7th Hammer<br><br>~Braellaar~<br>Super silly chanter <br>on 7th Hammer</td></tr>
